      <h2>Current Opportunities</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Apprenticeship Program:</strong> Gain hands-on experience working with experienced farmers and agribusiness professionals.</li>
        <li><strong>Fellowship Program:</strong> Engage in advanced agricultural projects with mentorship and financial support.</li>
        <li><strong>Entry-Level Farm Technicians:</strong> Join local farms working in planting, harvesting, and farm maintenance.</li>
        <li><strong>Urban Agriculture Coordinator:</strong> Lead community farming initiatives and urban garden programs.</li>
      </ul>
